00:43:20.434 --> 00:43:23.044
Your brother declared
him conqueror of worlds.

548
00:43:28.481 --> 00:43:30.121
The moment has arrived.

549
00:44:06.024 --> 00:44:08.474
That was eight years
before I was born.

550
00:44:22.556 --> 00:44:24.134
Were we foolish. Zor-El?

551
00:44:24.923 --> 00:44:27.517
Should we have
listened to your brother?

552
00:44:28.478 --> 00:44:30.478
We cannot send our daughter...

553
00:44:31.001 --> 00:44:33.001
...to another planet
to be a kind of god.

554
00:44:33.353 --> 00:44:35.353
We preserve this for a reason.

555
00:44:37.472 --> 00:44:41.519
We have to believe
that there is a future here.

556
00:44:47.574 --> 00:44:50.644
Kara. where are you?

557
00:45:00.084 --> 00:45:06.034
Honestly. I didn't have a clue that
Argo was different from any other planet.

558
00:45:07.978 --> 00:45:09.739
I thought we were lucky.

559
00:45:10.902 --> 00:45:14.837
But luck. almost by
definition. runs out.

560
00:45:24.395 --> 00:45:25.637
Tell me.

561
00:45:27.575 --> 00:45:30.200
When the city of
Argo separated...

562
00:45:30.207 --> 00:45:35.000
...it unearthed a crystalline
mineral from deep within the planet

563
00:45:35.712 --> 00:45:36.758
Kryptonite

564
00:45:38.014 --> 00:45:40.700
The ground is poisoned.

565
00:45:40.943 --> 00:45:43.436
It made all the
people of Argo sick...

566
00:45:43.881 --> 00:45:46.373
...and it is spreading.

567
00:45:48.053 --> 00:45:50.568
Can we do something?

568
00:46:22.343 --> 00:46:24.265
The radiation took
hold of me as well.

569
00:46:24.709 --> 00:46:26.920
I won't let it reach you.

570
00:46:30.280 --> 00:46:33.577
I found my brother's
sketches for the escape pod.

571
00:46:33.960 --> 00:46:35.702
I built one for you

572
00:46:37.301 --> 00:46:39.394
You will follow
your cousin. Kal-El.

573
00:46:40.928 --> 00:46:43.889
You will have a
new home on Earth.

574
00:46:47.065 --> 00:46:48.057
No

575
00:46:49.510 --> 00:46:51.112
This is my home.

576
00:46:51.417 --> 00:46:53.729
It is my only home.

577
00:46:57.711 --> 00:47:00.466
Let the radiation reach me.

578
00:47:01.178 --> 00:47:05.272
I will lie on the ground
next to you and mom.

579
00:47:08.633 --> 00:47:10.633
I am only one small life.

580
00:47:11.542 --> 00:47:15.542
What difference does
it make if I live or die?

581
00:47:15.792 --> 00:47:18.678
You are not just one small life.

582
00:47:19.779 --> 00:47:22.586
You are your mother's life.

583
00:47:24.109 --> 00:47:26.109
You are my life.

584
00:47:26.898 --> 00:47:30.447
You are our souls
unfolding into the future.

585
00:47:31.944 --> 00:47:33.092
My daughter...

586
00:47:33.584 --> 00:47:36.334
...this is the reason
for your existence.

587
00:47:49.061 --> 00:47:50.881
When I am gone...

588
00:47:52.124 --> 00:47:55.413
...promise me something.

589
00:47:56.592 --> 00:47:58.045
Of course. mother.

590
00:47:59.668 --> 00:48:01.334
Be good.

591
00:48:01.974 --> 00:48:06.106
That does not mean you are weak.

592
00:48:06.497 --> 00:48:09.560
Nor that you are kind.

593
00:48:12.121 --> 00:48:14.051
But you must be good.

594
00:48:22.842 --> 00:48:25.116
We do not choose our path

595
00:48:27.545 --> 00:48:30.279
Your path will be
one of great effort...

596
00:48:32.553 --> 00:48:34.553
...and of great purpose.

597
00:48:36.545 --> 00:48:41.834
Wherever you are going.
you will have great power.

598
00:48:43.339 --> 00:48:44.699
Use it to protect those...

599
00:48:44.996 --> 00:48:46.996
...who cannot
protect themselves.

600
00:48:48.667 --> 00:48:50.667
Trust yourself...

601
00:48:51.066 --> 00:48:52.746
...in knowing what is right.

602
00:49:33.999 --> 00:49:35.624
We are with you.

603
00:50:09.773 --> 00:50:10.773
So yeah.

604
00:50:13.669 --> 00:50:16.942
When I say I know what it's like.
I'm not talking out of my ass. Ruthye.

605
00:50:17.233 --> 00:50:18.783
Grief is a killer. you know?

606
00:50:18.808 --> 00:50:21.300
It can make you
want to break bad or...

607
00:50:21.968 --> 00:50:23.448
you know. get revenge. but...

608
00:50:27.115 --> 00:50:30.275
I don't think any of those things are
going to lead you to where you want to go.

609
00:50:34.081 --> 00:50:35.081
So what does?

610
00:50:36.828 --> 00:50:38.567
When did you stop feeling angry?

611
00:50:40.928 --> 00:50:41.928
Any day now.

612
00:50:42.100 --> 00:50:52.100
