614
00:50:42.100 --> 00:50:52.100
‫{\fs12} T.me/King_Subtitle

615
00:50:58.795 --> 00:51:01.612
Um. I'm just going
to go check on him.

616
00:51:02.342 --> 00:51:03.342
Stay here.

617
00:51:33.782 --> 00:51:34.842
Where's your friend?

618
00:51:35.048 --> 00:51:36.433
They come now.

619
00:51:36.622 --> 00:51:37.622
Sit.

620
00:51:50.753 --> 00:51:55.273
Recipe from my mother.
from her mother.etc...

621
00:51:57.188 --> 00:51:58.568
A little bitter.

622
00:51:59.355 --> 00:52:00.355
Thank you.

623
00:52:00.995 --> 00:52:01.995
Drink.

624
00:52:13.081 --> 00:52:14.641
How does your friend
know the brigands?

625
00:52:17.021 --> 00:52:19.884
We all know the brigands.

626
00:52:22.351 --> 00:52:23.001
But you said...

627
00:52:23.101 --> 00:52:25.800
Brigands come here. take girls.

628
00:52:26.261 --> 00:52:29.767
They come here to take our girl.

629
00:52:31.975 --> 00:52:32.975
Zarna.

630
00:52:34.450 --> 00:52:39.966
Yeah. your. um. your
daughter. the... the pictures.

631
00:52:42.290 --> 00:52:43.290
What did you give me?

632
00:52:44.470 --> 00:52:45.470
Sorry. sorry.

633
00:52:45.510 --> 00:52:46.110
Stop drinking.

634
00:52:46.377 --> 00:52:46.823
Stop drinking.

635
00:52:46.824 --> 00:52:49.367
Bomar. stop! She is our
daughter. we have no choice.

636
00:52:50.078 --> 00:52:52.245
Did you get this poison
from the brigands?

637
00:52:52.247 --> 00:52:53.667
No. I don't understand.

638
00:52:53.980 --> 00:52:55.101
You should be...

639
00:52:55.429 --> 00:52:56.482
...paralyzed.

640
00:52:57.147 --> 00:52:58.647
This is just really
going to suck.

641
00:53:10.267 --> 00:53:10.743
Milk

642
00:53:11.047 --> 00:53:11.513
Why?

643
00:53:12.067 --> 00:53:15.099
Well. it coats your stomach
if you've been poisoned.

644
00:53:15.540 --> 00:53:16.237
Come on. man.

645
00:53:16.237 --> 00:53:17.524
It's a white liquid.

646
00:53:17.524 --> 00:53:18.824
Help me out of here.

647
00:53:28.260 --> 00:53:29.407
What kind of milk is that?

648
00:53:29.407 --> 00:53:30.407
Chu-Kan

649
00:53:30.847 --> 00:53:31.847
Chu-Kan

650
00:53:32.302 --> 00:53:33.147
Oh. my God.

651
00:53:33.227 --> 00:53:34.227
Okay.

652
00:53:34.684 --> 00:53:35.974
So you sold me out for what?

653
00:53:35.999 --> 00:53:38.033
What are you getting in return?

654
00:53:39.141 --> 00:53:40.141
Speak.

655
00:53:40.321 --> 00:53:42.934
One girl for two girls.

656
00:54:15.590 --> 00:54:16.630
Hello

657
00:54:20.330 --> 00:54:21.450
Are you okay?

658
00:54:24.940 --> 00:54:27.120
I heard you were looking for me.

659
00:54:32.044 --> 00:54:34.266
Technically. you found me.

660
00:55:01.104 --> 00:55:04.066
Hey man. can you just
give me one second?

661
00:55:14.818 --> 00:55:16.818
Thanks...i needed that.

662
00:55:32.641 --> 00:55:36.081
You dropped your
puppy's ante-tongue.

663
00:55:40.514 --> 00:55:41.272
Kara !

664
00:55:44.014 --> 00:55:45.241
Help me !

665
00:55:51.775 --> 00:55:52.588
Stop !

666
00:55:54.611 --> 00:55:55.635
Kara !!!

667
00:56:16.233 --> 00:56:17.038
Sorry

668
00:56:20.173 --> 00:56:20.986
Are you drunk?

669
00:56:20.986 --> 00:56:21.986
No!

670
00:56:27.125 --> 00:56:31.067
Hey. she don't look
very poisoned to me. eh?

671
00:56:32.418 --> 00:56:33.536
Bring me their daughter.

672
00:56:33.629 --> 00:56:34.566
Now.

673
00:56:35.467 --> 00:56:36.300
You smell of vomit?

674
00:56:36.300 --> 00:56:37.620
It's because Mareck poisoned me.

675
00:56:38.957 --> 00:56:41.166
Oh. and I am fine.
thank you for asking.

676
00:57:09.253 --> 00:57:10.269
The brides !

677
00:57:10.550 --> 00:57:12.066
Catch them!

678
00:57:16.502 --> 00:57:17.502
Don't move.

679
00:57:51.102 --> 00:57:51.664
Run !

680
00:58:05.315 --> 00:58:09.435
Drom Baxton. there's a lot
of rich dipshits looking for you.

681
00:58:09.460 --> 00:58:10.900
Screw you. old man.

682
00:58:13.909 --> 00:58:14.909
Shit.

683
00:58:29.682 --> 00:58:31.409
A deal's a deal.

684
00:58:32.167 --> 00:58:33.401
She must die.

685
00:58:54.634 --> 00:58:55.634
Ouch.

686
00:59:03.382 --> 00:59:05.242
Aren't you the dips
from that diet bar?

687
00:59:05.256 --> 00:59:06.256
Funny.

688
00:59:07.100 --> 00:59:08.415
That's what I've
been calling you.

689
00:59:08.422 --> 00:59:09.422
Touche.

690
01:00:14.946 --> 01:00:16.326
Oh. that's ballsy.

691
01:00:16.659 --> 01:00:17.659
Drom Baxton !

692
01:00:17.999 --> 01:00:19.319
You just made me angry.

693
01:00:29.667 --> 01:00:31.034
Got ya. bastards!

694
01:00:40.662 --> 01:00:42.279
Sarna !

695
01:00:44.009 --> 01:00:45.967
Where are you?

696
01:00:46.562 --> 01:00:47.195
You okay?

697
01:00:47.402 --> 01:00:47.882
Yeah?

698
01:00:48.082 --> 01:00:49.222
Okay. get her out of here.

699
01:00:49.442 --> 01:00:50.175
She's the last one.

700
01:00:50.182 --> 01:00:50.517
Go!

701
01:00:50.736 --> 01:00:51.542
Go!

702
01:01:06.175 --> 01:01:07.480
Come on. Krem.

703
01:01:07.609 --> 01:01:08.909
Where's my antidote?

704
01:01:09.509 --> 01:01:11.909
You like to play games.

705
01:01:12.744 --> 01:01:14.667
I can play games.

706
01:01:21.840 --> 01:01:23.860
I can smell you.

707
01:01:43.607 --> 01:01:44.607
I told you not to move!

708
01:01:44.607 --> 01:01:45.367
I had him!

709
01:01:45.547 --> 01:01:46.547
Hide.

710
01:01:52.282 --> 01:01:53.235
Shit

711
01:01:56.237 --> 01:01:57.237
Sarna!

712
01:02:02.444 --> 01:02:02.844
No!

713
01:02:02.845 --> 01:02:03.845
No!

714
01:02:04.704 --> 01:02:05.704
Stop!

715
01:02:37.747 --> 01:02:38.507
They're dead!

716
01:02:38.532 --> 01:02:40.667
Because you did not let
me do what had to be done!

717
01:02:40.667 --> 01:02:42.933
Okay. Ruthye. I'm not
letting you kill that man.

718
01:02:42.933 --> 01:02:43.933
Why not?

719
01:02:44.073 --> 01:02:45.793
Look at the suffering
he leaves in his wake!

720
01:02:45.893 --> 01:02:46.838
Why does he get to be alive?

721
01:02:46.863 --> 01:02:48.833
Okay. okay. stop freaking out!

722
01:02:48.833 --> 01:02:49.833
Get off!

723
01:02:50.143 --> 01:02:52.466
Don't tell me not to freak out!

724
01:02:53.068 --> 01:02:54.068
I'm allowed.

725
01:02:54.788 --> 01:02:55.788
Tell me why.

726
01:02:55.841 --> 01:02:57.200
Because it will mess you up.

727
01:02:57.581 --> 01:02:59.413
You think it'll make
you feel better?

728
01:02:59.413 --> 01:03:00.413
It won't!

729
01:03:00.706 --> 01:03:02.767
It'll haunt you for
the rest of your life!

730
01:03:03.099 --> 01:03:04.099
Is that what you want?

731
01:03:06.052 --> 01:03:07.532
So the alternative
is to be like you?

732
01:03:08.592 --> 01:03:09.592
Constantly...

733
01:03:09.632 --> 01:03:11.852
Leaving your planet to
drink yourself into a stupor?

734
01:03:12.719 --> 01:03:15.567
Drunk all of the time so you
never have to feel anything?

735
01:03:15.567 --> 01:03:16.067
Guess what?

736
01:03:16.492 --> 01:03:18.500
I. too. want to free
myself of this pain.

737
01:03:18.922 --> 01:03:20.500
And I do not want
to be like you.

738
01:03:21.372 --> 01:03:22.372
Okay.

739
01:03:23.812 --> 01:03:26.132
Then why don't you go
find whatever dimensional

740
01:03:26.132 --> 01:03:28.490
portal he just passed
through all by yourself?

741
01:04:49.733 --> 01:04:50.213
Hey!

742
01:04:50.667 --> 01:04:51.146
Squidward!

743
01:04:51.532 --> 01:04:52.332
Where are the brigands?

744
01:04:52.479 --> 01:04:53.479
No idea.

745
01:04:53.519 --> 01:04:54.519
Really?

746
01:04:55.479 --> 01:04:56.233
Bullshit.

747
01:04:56.382 --> 01:04:58.933
I have less than 24
hours to save my dog.

748
01:04:59.106 --> 01:05:02.669
So you tell me where the brigands are
and I won't turn you into a hand puppet.

749
01:05:03.089 --> 01:05:03.569
Okay?

750
01:05:06.703 --> 01:05:07.703
Okay.

751
01:05:09.663 --> 01:05:10.501
OK

752
01:05:11.167 --> 01:05:12.834
We will have to wear these.

753
01:05:19.190 --> 01:05:20.190
Let's go.

754
01:05:55.481 --> 01:05:57.437
This is as close as we get.

755
01:06:42.837 --> 01:06:45.673
PLANET: BARENTON SOLAR
CATEGORY: GREEN AND YELLOW

756
01:07:06.993 --> 01:07:07.993
Hi there.

757
01:07:10.700 --> 01:07:12.580
I've been tracking your
ship for the last month.

758
01:07:12.670 --> 01:07:14.567
I believe you're from Krypton?

759
01:07:14.953 --> 01:07:16.013
And so am I.

760
01:07:17.693 --> 01:07:18.693
Clark.

761
01:07:19.843 --> 01:07:21.178
I don't understand
what you are saying.

762
01:07:22.108 --> 01:07:23.483
Where am i?

763
01:07:23.610 --> 01:07:25.610
I am on Earth?

764
01:07:26.749 --> 01:07:27.987
Are you Kal-El?

765
01:07:28.207 --> 01:07:29.277
Oh. I'm sorry.

766
01:07:29.397 --> 01:07:30.697
I don't... Oh. I don't...

767
01:07:32.167 --> 01:07:33.561
I don't speak Kryptonian.

768
01:07:33.561 --> 01:07:35.666
I never....shoot.

769
01:07:35.687 --> 01:07:38.817
I... I wasn't raised there.
so... I wasn't raised there.

770
01:07:38.817 --> 01:07:39.817
Why am I talking louder?

771
01:07:39.877 --> 01:07:40.877
Uh. let me help you.

772
01:07:41.451 --> 01:07:43.272
Krypto. behave yourself.

773
01:07:44.022 --> 01:07:44.581
Be good.

774
01:07:44.733 --> 01:07:45.966
It's a feisty little guy.

775
01:07:46.883 --> 01:07:47.883
He's cute.

776
01:07:48.856 --> 01:07:49.856
Is it okay if I...

777
01:07:55.267 --> 01:07:56.807
Watch your step there.

778
01:07:57.189 --> 01:07:58.209
Might be slippery. so...

779
01:07:58.759 --> 01:07:59.569
Is this. um...

780
01:07:59.669 --> 01:08:00.669
I'll grab it.

781
01:08:02.109 --> 01:08:03.109
Okay.

782
01:08:04.309 --> 01:08:05.309
Ah. yeah.

783
01:08:05.362 --> 01:08:06.362
Pretty cool. huh?

784
01:08:08.589 --> 01:08:08.989
Don't worry.

785
01:08:08.989 --> 01:08:10.466
We don't actually live here.

786
01:08:11.009 --> 01:08:13.233
There's a lot more to
Earth than just this place.

787
01:08:14.219 --> 01:08:14.946
Big city.

788
01:08:15.239 --> 01:08:16.480
Lots of stuff to do.

789
01:08:16.739 --> 01:08:17.139
Bowling.

790
01:08:17.164 --> 01:08:18.164
That's fun.

791
01:08:18.293 --> 01:08:19.967
Uh. it was a big
adjustment for me.

792
01:08:20.073 --> 01:08:21.169
You know. coming from Kansas.

793
01:08:21.193 --> 01:08:24.274
You know. I'm a small-town kind
of guy. but. uh... You know Kansas?

794
01:08:24.878 --> 01:08:25.197
No.

795
01:08:25.304 --> 01:08:26.344
Why would you know Kansas?

796
01:08:26.444 --> 01:08:27.444
What am I...

797
01:08:28.925 --> 01:08:31.045
You can't understand a
word that I'm saying right now.

798
01:08:33.128 --> 01:08:34.128
It's okay.

799
01:08:34.416 --> 01:08:35.416
You will one day.

800
01:08:35.805 --> 01:08:39.067
And you'll also learn to love
this place. just like I have.

801
01:08:40.059 --> 01:08:41.059
Promise.

802
01:08:44.534 --> 01:08:46.461
Why is he in his underwear?

803
01:08:46.561 --> 01:08:48.361
Oh. I should mention...

804
01:08:50.105 --> 01:08:54.933
Your powers are gonna start
kicking in... right about... now.

805
01:09:08.993 --> 01:09:10.829
How can this be my home?

806
01:10:16.212 --> 01:10:17.732
I thought that the
shelter might help.

807
01:10:18.433 --> 01:10:19.433
Was I right?

808
01:10:21.346 --> 01:10:22.534
What did you...

809
01:10:22.543 --> 01:10:25.867
I saw you boarding that man's
ship. so I snuck up into the cargo hold.

810
01:10:26.453 --> 01:10:27.453
What's this place?

811
01:10:31.693 --> 01:10:32.693
It's my prison.

812
01:10:34.108 --> 01:10:37.003
I'm afraid it's now that
the planet orbits between...

813
01:10:37.959 --> 01:10:38.959
two suns.

814
01:10:40.731 --> 01:10:42.101
And that the green sun...

815
01:10:43.785 --> 01:10:44.865
can kill me.

816
01:10:48.533 --> 01:10:50.067
Krem left your ship on Bilquis.

817
01:10:50.188 --> 01:10:51.188
And I found this.

818
01:10:53.200 --> 01:10:54.360
I thought that it might help.

819
01:10:57.945 --> 01:11:01.100
It's just a stupid suit. Ruthye.

820
01:11:03.746 --> 01:11:05.066
It doesn't do anything.

821
01:11:16.630 --> 01:11:17.646
My dog...

822
01:11:24.059 --> 01:11:25.059
